# Cloudflare static-assets headers.
# Always revalidate the HTML so a fresh deploy is visible immediately rather
# than being served from a stale edge/browser cache. Hashed-name assets could
# cache longer, but these filenames are stable, so revalidate them too —
# Cloudflare still answers with 304s, so the cost is negligible.
/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
